snippet.title: Two Point Hospital: JUMBO Edition | Console Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Two Point Hospital: JUMBO Edition is OUT NOW on consoles! 

Join 3 million happy players in our most gigantic release so far, with four expansion packs and two massive item packs included:

Two Point Hospital: Bigfoot
Two Point Hospital: Pebberley Island
Two Point Hospital: Close Encounters
Two Point Hospital: Off the Grid
Retro Items Pack
Exhibition Items Pack
